Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:07.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:23.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:29.22,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.69,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:37.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather comes fluttering\ndown, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:44.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:54.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:01:01.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:08.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:14.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:23.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:27.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.45,0:01:34.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:35.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:42.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have come here from Heaven to grant\nyou a wish, Mr. Keiichi Morisato, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:47.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, I was trying to\ncall Aoyama, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:51.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got connected to some weird place\nand a girl appeared out of that mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...telling me she'll grant me a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:57.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, come to think of it,\nwho'd she come out of the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:00.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that,\nbut she's calling herself a goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:03.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Goddess Help Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:16.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess 1st Class, 2nd Category,\NUnlimited License. My name, Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:19.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello, I'm Keiichi Morisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:26.76,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Those Who Believe Shall Find\NSalvation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:40.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had a girl over before,\nso this is all I can offer you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:43.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderfully kind of you... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here... this is my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:56.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of business would a\ngoddess like you have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:00.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We goddesses have a mission,\nwhich is to do what we can to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...rescue those in distress,\nlike yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am here at the request\nof Mr. Keiichi Morisato, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:13.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Request? I don't remember\nmaking any request...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did receive your phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that? That was a wrong number!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Up in Heaven...{\i0}\nI was just trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:26.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...we watch over all of the lives\nbeing led in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:30.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Needless to say, that includes you,\NMr. Keiichi Morisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:34.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your fortitude in the\nface of misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness towards others...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly worthy\nof the highest praise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it's nothing special, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:47.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The balance between your fortune\nand misfortune has been so lopsided...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:50.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that it has exceeded all limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:54.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, this triggered\NYggdrasil into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:59.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have earned the right\nto receive Heaven's Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:02.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by ''Grace''?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:06.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It means that your wish will be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:15.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, keep in mind that\nyou will be limited to just one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:19.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can grant you\nanything you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And only one wish, for that matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:28.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, please tell me\nwhat you wish for!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I get just one wish, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:37.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can ask\nfor something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:42.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If your wish is to become wealthy,\nwe will be happy to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...bestow riches upon you,\nmore than you could ever use...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...in an entire lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:47.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:52.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And should you desire the\ndestruction of the world, we can make...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that happen as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:08.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, we would never appear before\nanyone with that sort of wish in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to believe your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:13.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're not from some\NNew Age religious cult...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:17.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...out to swindle me into buying\nan expensive vase, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I would never utter such\nfalsehoods to you. Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:25.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...we goddesses do not tell lies\nunder any circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:29.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you can't\neven tell the smallest lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:30.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:34.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, tell me, do you think I'm cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See, you can lie, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:44.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what I just said wasn't a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:47.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. You're really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:54.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The seniors must've\ncooked this up to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:57.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...fun of me because\nI've never had a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:02.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:06.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you can read my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:10.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but what I don't understand is\nwhy you, Mr. Keiichi Morisato...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:13.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...have never had a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:19.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stand up for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:31.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now you get it, don't you? Five foot\nthree just doesn't cut it nowadays...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:36.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just because someone's tall\ndoesn't mean that he's attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:40.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from these overly thick\neyebrows, I have a forgettable face...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is what makes you unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think it becomes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:53.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sum of my entire fortune...\nand it's not long after New Year's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:57.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty lame, huh?\NHow uncool is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:03.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One's financial status must never\nbe equated with one's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:09.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do not believe one is less attractive as\na person because he has no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:11.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:21.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly you have some kind of complex\nabout your outward appearance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:25.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly does that have\nto do with a person's worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:30.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You possess something of great value...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:33.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For example, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Love that's bursting at the seams...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:56.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Old though they may be, and though no\none would give them a second look...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:00.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...they're all in perfect working order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the monitor turning on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the video heads turning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:10.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These are all such happy sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:14.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They know that you will use them and\nthat they are fortunate to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:31.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And it is all because you do not\njudge them by looks or capacity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:35.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because you shower them\nwith such affection!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:49.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, then... I guess I'll tell you\nwhat I want you to grant me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:52.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you've reached\na decision, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:55.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a goddess like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:57.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to always...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:58.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:09.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know. I guess that was\na rude thing to say to someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I just met,\neven if you are a goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:34.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I just said that for the heck of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:55.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I need to borrow your\nphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:19.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? This is Belldandy speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:22.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The wish that was\njust submitted now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean that's\na viable request, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, wait... Almighty One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,''Almighty One''?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with my phone,\nanyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish has been duly granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:40.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So my wish is going to come true.\NThat's good... good to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:47.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They granted my wish...\nfor you to always stay with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:54.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means that I can stay with you\nforever, Mr. Keiichi Morisato, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They accepted that wish of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:15.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has been duly processed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:24.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This will allow me to stay by your side\nforever, Mr. Keiichi Morisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:28.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're going\nto be living with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are some days I'll be at college.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money!\NAre you okay with being poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:36.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:39.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I'm gonna have to work part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:51.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By my side...\NA goddess always by my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:57.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be what they\ncall cohabitating, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:12:01.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually going to live\nunder the same roof as a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:08.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've made your\nfavorite dish tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:12.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I love more than\nanything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:17.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease me like that, Keiichi, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, shouldn't\nwe go on a date first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:24.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take a romantic spin along\nthe beach or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:27.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got this bike just so\nI could take you for a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:29.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! How lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:33.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go, and gaze upon\nthe sunset at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:43.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up. She's a goddess,\nso it should be more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I obtained this broom just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:54.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's take it to go\nsee the sunset at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi Morisato, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:05.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi Morisato, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:08.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just read my mind now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:16.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's for real, then.\nI'm going to live with a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:21.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how can I make her live in\na dinky 6-mat room like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:25.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be hit with divine retribution?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:32.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that should do it, don'tcha think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:35.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:39.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh!\nIf the seniors find out about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Women aren't allowed in this dorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:48.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that shouldn't be a problem.\NAfter all, I'm a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:53.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not the point!\nI need you to get out of this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:56.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there will be trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:02.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There will be even more trouble\nif the seniors find out about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:06.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the System Force takes effect\nwhenever wishes are granted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and there's no defying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The System Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:15.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is something that\nI am powerless to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:20.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on resisting it, then\nI'm afraid you'll only come to grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of grief?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:30.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it even more terrible than\ngoing against the seniors' orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hold down the fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:40.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Force\nhas already come into play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}\NMorisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:48.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato! You little bastard,\nhow dare you sneak a woman into...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:53.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...our male-only sanctuary\nand then push her to the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:57.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you're prepared\nto face the music for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:00.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there are all these\ncircumstances, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:04.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He who dares break the dorm rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gets thrown out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's human mikoshi time!\NCarry him out, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:16.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wasshoi! Wasshoi! Wasshoi!\NWasshoi! Wasshoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:31.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, why am I not surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:43.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The System Force kicks in when the\ntwo of us are about to get torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:47.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:51.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My bike has been acting up lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:56.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now where did I leave\nthe keys to my bike? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:06.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's your reward for holding down\nthe fort! We fixed it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:10.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a new chapter in your life!\NSo we're sending you off in style!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:15.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send the rest of your stuff as\nsoon as you find a new place, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:22.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, what the heck\nshould we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:31.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have been evicted from your dorm\nbecause of me, Keiichi Morisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:35.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll figure something out!\NBy the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:39.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you call me something other\nthan Keiichi Morisato or ''sir''?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:43.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot grant such a wish, you have\nalready been granted one just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:49.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I'll give you an\nextra bonus, just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:08.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:12.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A man's not a man until he sets off\non a journey like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can we crash at your place tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Great timing!{\i0}\NCan we crash at your place tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:29.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just keep going 'til morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a girl with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:37.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, that guy's easy pickings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:41.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said it! That Morisato's got\na lot of nerve...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:44.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rob him for all he's got\nin front of his girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:45.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:50.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've cleaned up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:18:00.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's my Goddess\nof Fortune, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:05.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep on the street, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you do something in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:19.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I need a favor from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:25.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hasegawa!\NAt least hear me out, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:30.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you put her up, just for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:35.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You come to my door at this late hour ,\nand it's for a favor like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:40.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Hasegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:45.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But only your woman friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:48.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! I can crash somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:51.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, that means that you'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I know\nhow tired you must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But knowing that you\nhave no place to stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:01.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry it up.\nI have an early morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:04.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go inside, Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:11.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I get it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, it's the System Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}\NDon't tell me, it's the System Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:26.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here to flaunt your affection\nfor each other, go somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:30.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute! Hasegawa!\nI can explain all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:45.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:52.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nekomi Institute of Technology{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't get in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:19.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:23.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've never been to a\nplace like this before, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:27.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you around\nsometime during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:30.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be lots of people.\nIt's livelier and fun to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:31.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It does sound like a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:41.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I gotta rig up\nsomeplace for us to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A goddess, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:08.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just say that I dialed the phone\nand out she came from the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:11.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who would buy a story like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:15.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, she's so sweet and\nupbeat and so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:18.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it means I can live\nwith a girl like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:20.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:24.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you and I will\nbe living together, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:29.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that every day will be wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:32.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:36.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you had a long day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:40.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stay up all night\nto make sure you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:43.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You get a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:53.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never experienced\nanything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:57.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't we talk some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:59.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:04.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to tell me more\nabout yourself, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:09.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sure like to hear\nabout Heaven and all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:13.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! Now then,\nI'll start with the questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:15.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:18.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My parents and my sister\nlive in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hokkaido? And where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:39.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:50.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:23:00.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:06.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:13.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:16.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:22.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:28.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:34.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for you\ngives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:40.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:45.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:00.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are wandering souls,\nthose who seek the Promised Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:05.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go where the goddess directs you. You\nwill find a place that will ease your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:08.38,AMG next episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ah! Apprenticeship,\NHome, and the Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:11.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are the rules about a\ngoddess living in a temple?
